  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ずいぶん料理のレパートリーが増えたね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like our repertoire of recipes have increased.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>食うもんが増えんのはいいよな、
もっと増やそうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Having more to eat is best. Let's find more.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも今は研究してるヒマないし、
教えてもらわないとね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But we don't really have time to experiment new dishes,
nor get someone to teach us more.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもさ、教えてくれるヤツいんだろ、
あの……なんだっけ？　すばらしきワンダーシェフ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't there someone right here? Uhh...what's their
name again...? The Wonderful Wonder Chef?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『すばらしき味の世界』、でしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wasn't it the "wonderful world of flavors"?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どっちでもいいけど、あいつら、
変装して待ち伏せしてんなら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatever! Anyways, those guys are probably hiding
somewhere in a disguise.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>一緒に来てくれればいいのに、
オレらの料理番としてさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It'd be better if they joined us as a personal
cook or something.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、歩きづらいかもしれない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...It might be hard to walk around with them...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>歩きづらい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do you mean?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だって、あんな変装の人と
街とか一緒に歩けないよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can't just expect us to walk around town
with someone dressed like that, can you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_190_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>見た目よりうまい飯、だろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who cares, at least we'd have good food!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
